    "3": {
      "title": "Amber Armor",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Amber_Armor\">Amber Armor</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Amber&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Amber Armor\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Amber_Armor_Male.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/7e/SR-item-Amber_Armor_Male.jpg/200px-SR-item-Amber_Armor_Male.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/7/7e/SR-item-Amber_Armor_Male.jpg/300px-SR-item-Amber_Armor_Male.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/7/7e/SR-item-Amber_Armor_Male.jpg/400px-SR-item-Amber_Armor_Male.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Amber_Armor_Male.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A male <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Nord\" title=\"Skyrim:Nord\">Nord</a> wearing Amber Armor</div></div></div>\n<p>Amber <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Armor\" title=\"Skyrim:Armor\">armor</a> is a variety of light armor which is superior to standard <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dragonscale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Dragonscale\">dragonscale</a> armor, making it the second most powerful light armor you can craft in the game before the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dragon_Items\" title=\"Skyrim:Dragon Items\">Studded Dragonscale Armor</a> from the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Dragonscale\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Dragonscale\">Alternative Armors - Dragonscale</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Creation Club\">Creation</a>.\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable striped\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Armor Rating\"><img alt=\"Armor Rating\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/22px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/33px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/44px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"3\" class=\"unsortable\">Raw Materials\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Delta\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Ratio\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Refined_Amber.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"